data.description: Nestled within the highly sought after neighborhood of The Forest at East Lake, this newer construction home has all the features of your dream home and Intown living. Greeted by a spacious open concept floor plan flooded with natural light and captivating wooded views, the main level features inviting living and dining areas, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The chef of the home will fall in love with the modern kitchen boasting oversized kitchen island, Stainless Steel appliances, pantry and abundant counter and storage space. The living room is the heart of the home, complete with a cozy gas fireplace and high ceilings adorned with beams, adding a touch of rustic charm to the modern design of the home. Enjoy slow mornings with coffee and late afternoons with a good book on the screened in porch overlooking the backyard. The front room provides a great option as a sitting room or guest bedroom and head to the upper level where the lofted landing creates another space for a family room, home gym or bright office. Retreat to your expansive primary suite with an en-suite bath featuring soaking tub, glass enclosed tile shower and walk-in closet. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms share a bathroom room and a dedicated laundry room rounds out the upper level. Convenience meets functionality with the inclusion of a 2-car garage with utility sink, ensuring ample parking and storage space for your vehicles and outdoor gear. The unfinished basement presents endless possibilities, framed and plumbed for a bedroom and bathroom along with living space and wet bar offering the potential for expansion and customization to suit your needs. Enjoy summer BBQS on the deck or let the pups run free in the private fenced-in backyard. Conveniently located near East Lake shopping and dining, experience the epitome of modern living in this idyllic sanctuary, where every day feels like a retreat amidst nature's splendor.
